text: int main ( ) { int t ; long int a , b , i , gcd , lcm ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { scanf ( "%ld %ld" , & a , & b ) ; if ( a > b ) { for ( i = 1 ; i <= b ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } } else { for ( i = 1 ; i <= a ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%ld %ld\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
